description: Two-ply bathroom tissue features an environmentally friendly design that's made with a high percentage of post-consumer material to provide a sustainable choice for your employees and guests. Strong, absorbent material offers reliable performance to minimize wasteful use. Each roll is individually wrapped to protect from dust and debris when stored. Tissue is perfect for retail shops, industrial facilities, schools, foodservice venues and more. Bathroom tissue is designed for use in standard toilet roll dispensers (sold separately).
